{"id":614335,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/07/【立此存照】爱国有罪-民间爱国遭遇重大挫折/","date":"2019-07-23T04:20:09Z","modified":"2019-07-23T06:30:30Z","title":"【立此存照】爱国有罪 “民间爱国”遭遇重大挫折","content":"<p>7月23日，知名“民间爱国组织”帝吧集团军拟发起“海外出征行动”，声援与元朗白衣人握手的香港建制派立法会议员何君尧，然而行动发起后帝吧“高层”发起人却遭有关部门谈话，疑似收到取消行动的指示或有关压力，最终该行动提前终止。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/EAIF-XWVUAAZkFW.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-614337\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/EAIF-XWVUAAZkFW.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"743\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/EAIF-XWVUAAZkFW.jpeg 1184w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/EAIF-XWVUAAZkFW-222x300.jpeg 222w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/EAIF-XWVUAAZkFW-768x1038.jpeg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/EAIF-XWVUAAZkFW-758x1024.jpeg 758w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/EAIVah4UEAE7S8W.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-614338\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/EAIVah4UEAE7S8W.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"571\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/EAIVah4UEAE7S8W.jpeg 986w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/EAIVah4UEAE7S8W-289x300.jpeg 289w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/EAIVah4UEAE7S8W-768x798.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\">7月24日，@帝吧官微 宣布“编辑不再负责微博更新”，一小时后又表示“仅停更休息一周”，暂不清楚是否其账号受到了接管。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/Jietu20190723-120348@2x.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-614342\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/Jietu20190723-120348@2x.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"122\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/Jietu20190723-120348@2x.jpg 1192w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/Jietu20190723-120348@2x-300x66.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/Jietu20190723-120348@2x-768x170.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/Jietu20190723-120348@2x-1024x227.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/Jietu20190723-120417@2x.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-614343\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/Jietu20190723-120417@2x.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"393\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/Jietu20190723-120417@2x.jpg 1186w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/Jietu20190723-120417@2x-300x215.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/Jietu20190723-120417@2x-768x549.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/Jietu20190723-120417@2x-1024x732.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>以下为帝吧官方微博曾发布的“声援香港警察”、“拥护一国两制”的相关行动图片，并曾将“海外出征行动”定于7月23日晚8点。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/Jietu20190723-115601@2x.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-614340\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/Jietu20190723-115601@2x.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"398\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/Jietu20190723-115601@2x.jpg 1196w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/Jietu20190723-115601@2x-300x217.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/Jietu20190723-115601@2x-768x556.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/Jietu20190723-115601@2x-1024x741.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/007EpNlsgy1g57mefqfomj30u018zwqj.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-614341\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/007EpNlsgy1g57mefqfomj30u018zwqj.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"674\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/007EpNlsgy1g57mefqfomj30u018zwqj.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/007EpNlsgy1g57mefqfomj30u018zwqj-200x300.jpg 200w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/07/007EpNlsgy1g57mefqfomj30u018zwqj-683x1024.jpg 683w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>由于&#8221;帝吧集团军”通常将其行动的方式设定为翻墙至Facebook等海外平台进行“统一刷评”，目前暂不清楚是否因大规模的翻墙行动本身而受到压制。在此之前，<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/01/%e3%80%90%e7%9c%9f%e7%90%86%e9%83%a8%e3%80%91-%e5%b8%9d%e5%90%a7%e5%87%ba%e5%be%81%e4%ba%8b%e4%bb%b6/\">【真理部】“帝吧出征”事件</a> 显示，有关部门对帝吧出征所带来的翻墙技术大面积传播及不可控的负面评论产生有所忌惮。</p>\n<p><iframe title=\"7.21民陣大遊行 | 親北京議員何君堯為毆打市民的地區社團人士打氣\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/aciSq8cnhWM?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/03/432213/\">【立此存照】帝吧出征维珍航空 认错公司无辜躺枪</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/07/%e7%9f%a5%e4%b9%8e%e6%97%a5%e6%8a%a5%ef%bd%9c%e5%b8%9d%e5%90%a7%e9%a3%8e%e4%ba%91%ef%bc%9a%e4%ba%92%e8%81%94%e7%bd%91%e6%84%a4%e6%80%92%e9%9d%92%e5%b9%b4%e6%b5%81%e5%8f%98%e5%8f%b2/\">知乎日报｜帝吧风云：互联网愤怒青年流变史</a></p></blockquote>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[38564,38551,30038,30059,38643,38526]}